When this card is Normal or Special Summoned: You can add 1 "Star Seraph" monster from your Deck to your hand, except "Star Seraph Scepter". An Xyz Monster that was Xyz Summoned using 3 or more monsters you control as Xyz Materials (including this card on the field) gains this effect.‚óè When this card is Xyz Summoned: You can target 1 other card on the field; destroy that card, and if you do, you can draw 1 card.
